      "content": "thanks. i tried to give the fan a little nudge with a stick while it was humming and it started spinning up for a second but then it just died again. it's almost like something is electrical or preventing it from getting enough power to start the motor. is there a specific part that usually fails and causes that kind of intermittent behavior?",
